    "body": "`fundrawtransaction`, `send`, `sendall`, and `walletcreatefundedpsbt` all document `maxconf` as `Optional::OMITTED`, while the sibling parameter `minconf` explicitly documents its default of `0`. The actual default for `maxconf` is `9999999` (`DEFAULT_MAX_DEPTH` in `src/wallet/coincontrol.h`).\n\n`listunspent` already documents this correctly:\n```cpp\n{\"maxconf\", RPCArg::Type::NUM, RPCArg::Default{9999999}, \"The maximum confirmations to filter\"},\n```\n\nThis PR applies the same pattern to the four affected RPCs for consistency.",
    "labels": [
